sequence for MTN13, choose the one for the PA3025 and patch the
following locations:

2172	CLRSCN:	02	; Count (length of this home/clear screen sequence)
		1F	; First char of sequence
		1F	; Second char
		00	; with room up to next label - leave one 0.

217D	INVON:	03	; Length of Inverse Video (or dim) ON
		1B	; First char
		4F	; Second
		31	; Next, etc, as above
		00

2184	INVOFF:	03	; Length of Inverse Video (or dim) OFF (normal)
		1B	; First char
		4F	; Next
		30	; Last
		00

